 Dawn stood infront of a fire that was being built. The early morning sun shown down as she prepared the center of the village for the intiation of a new amazon. Near a stage like setting, was a tiny table and on that table a shamaness was preparing a dagger, sacred for the cermony. To the otherside of her, many amazons were working around to clear things out of the way, and set up the ground so that it was clean. <br>
<br>
 Tonight was a full moon, and tonight would be the night that Angel was made a real Amazon. <br>
<br>
 Taking a deep breath, Dawn continued to watch. This would be her first time intiating anyone into her tribe.. making her Angel a full amazon.<br>
<br>
 &lt;Angel&gt;<br>
<br>
 Angel had road into the village the night before, and now walked up to Dawn, standing at her side. Angel had idley thrust her hands into her jean pockets, and stood nervously watching. This was a big step for her, but it was something she wanted to do.. something that would make her complete. <br>
<br>
 Glancing around, Angel finally realized how out of place she looked. A smooth grin slipped across her lips.. perhaps she'd be getting another make over!<br>
<br>
 &lt;Dawn&gt;<br>
<br>
 As if reading the teens mind, looked over at Angel and nodded.<br>
<br>
 &quot;There will be wardrobe changes.. as soon as some more athelfi get here. . we'll start.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn turned on her heel and began walking toward her hut.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Go to your hut, get rested. An amazon will fetch you later&quot; <p>
