<br>
She had been a nervous wreck at her coronation, so she'd assumed Angel would feel the same way and had descided to come early and see Angel before her intiation.<br>
<br>
After taking her blonde stallion, which was a birthday present from the Queen of Orio-Pata herself, she made her way to Angel's hut, which she knew somehow, and knocked lightly on the door. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 336<br> <font color=#939393>(9/9/01 8:23:39 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Angel's intiation into Orio-Pata</span><hr size=1>  &lt;Angel&gt;<br>
