<br>
&quot;Trust me, I know how you feel. I was scared stiff at my coronation, but there's nothing to be nervous about. You'll be amazing, I know you will.&quot;<br>
<br>
She gave a brief nod confidently before continueing,<br>
<br>
&quot;And before you know it, the iniation's over, and you're celebrating with the other Amazons, and you have a new family that will stand by you forever, and you're a part of a strong, wonderful, honorable, nation, and you're a perfect addition to it.&quot;<br>
<br>
