<br>
Alysia appeared behind Belle smiling lightly.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes Belle, but remember you had a coronation. That is much different than an initiation. An Amazon is initiated when they are sixteen years or older. You've still got another year.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled to her daughter then to Angel.<br>
<br>
&quot;Congrats Angel, an Initiation is a sacred ceremony, you only have one per tribe.&quot;<br>
<br>
She too remembered hers into the Amazon Nation as a whole. It was overwhelming and very special.<br>
<br>
<br>
   <br>
<br>
Cyane had appeared a while earlier than the others. She was there to give any services to Queen Dawn that was needed.<br>
She appeared before the Queen in her usual ceremonial Amazon leathers and bowed her head.<br>
<br>
&quot;I am at your service Vasilissa.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
    <br>
<br>
Wulf had been in his hut alone all morning in deep meditation praying for the spirit of the Ancients to be with Angel at this time for it was sacred and special.<br>
<br>
Later on he had bathed in the river and prepared himself in his own leathers and helped some of the others assist with the fire. He would not be a large part of the actual traditions seeing that he was male, but he was an Amazon Prince and was here for Angel. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 338<br> <font color=#939393>(9/10/01 3:21:07 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Angel's intiation into Orio-Pata</span><hr size=1>  &lt;Dawn&gt;<br>
<br>
 Dawn glanced to Cyane and smiled lightly, motioning to those already at work and her son as well.<br>
<br>
 &quot;As you can see.. we've got alot of what we need, being done.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn glanced around once more, before turning back to face Cyane.<br>
<br>
 &quot;But as a shamaness.. I believe we could use you. Have you ever done an intiation, Cyane?&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
