<br>
 Those blue pools glanced to Aly, and she nodded, then glanced back to Belle.<br>
<br>
 &quot;I was told to get ready.. for the intiation.. and that a few amazons would be here to help me.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Angel stopped briefly.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Are you two it?&quot;<br>
<br>
