After most of the things were set up for Angel's initiation, Wulf walked around Orio-Pata just observing. Few of the Amazons chose not to attend seeing that they weren't old enough. He passed by the training yards and smiled seeing the progression that had occured since he had left.<br>
<br>
<br>
      <br>
<br>
She sighed softly and frowned a bit.<br>
<br>
&quot;Sadly Vasilissa no, I haven't.  I am however willing to assist in anyway possible.&quot;<br>
<br>
Though Belle and Angel were closer, Cyane still felt like Angel was a good friend of hers, and she wanted to be apart of this.<br>
<br>
<br>
