<br>
 Dawn nodded to Cyane, and grinned lightly.<br>
<br>
 &quot;Then you can help an old Queen, with something she has never done herself. I need to plan this.. and I could use some creative ideas.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Dawn motioned to a table with tribal scrolls from other places on the intiation laws, and what is required as well as a blank one, for ideas to be wrote on.<br>
<br>
 Glancing off to another side, Dawn grabbed a leather messenger bag, and tossed it to a young amazon. Then directed her to take the contents to Angel. . so that she may have someone ready her for the ceremony. . . someone she would feel comfortable with.<br>
<br>
 &lt;The Amazon&gt;<br>
<br>
 The young girl nodded, taking the bag and heading off to Angel's new hut. Once there she cleared her throat, to get the attention of Belle and Aly. Once she did.. she held out the bag.<br>
<br>
 Inside, was a short leather skirt, that was slit up the side for smooth fighting, and then a corsit type top that laced tightly up the back. Then there was one sheath.. with a dagger.. it could be placed where ever on the body. As well as various jewelry.<br>
<br>
 &lt;Angel&gt;<br>
<br>
 Angel took the bag glancing to Alysia and Belle after the young girl told of Dawn's orders. Tossing it on the bed . . she glanced to them with a pleading look.<br>
<br>
 &quot;It looks like its up to you two.. and Belle knows how hopeless I am with fashion.&quot;<br>
<br>
 Angel grinned sheepishly.. glancing between the Queen and Princess.<br>
<br>
 &lt;A Demonic Tiger&gt;<br>
<br>
 Wulf was always welcome in the village of Orio-Pata.. he was afterall their prince. And when the mother of most of the demonic tiger cubs, seen the Queen's child come around.. it lumbered out of a shady area.. and padded to his feet. Purring loudly as she glanced upward at him. Obviously she was happy to see him.  <p>
